reviews.review_text: Aaaaaaaaah Now THIS is a Matrix.  Flawless sound. Is it slow as mentioned in the previous review?  Perhaps just a tad, but only if you really listen for it (at least for my aged ears).  Show is a total blow out. Fall/Winter 79 produced some of my favorite shows.  Energy was incredible and Jerry seemed to be on a mission to lay waste to every venue they played.  By all means crank this one up to 11.
Every Listen makes it better Man, I cannot say enough about this show - jams galore - I'm in the middle of estimated and its divine!
